        <abstract>
            <p>Observations on expression and variation in Asian peoples: when colour of beard and hair differ, beard is always lighter. Differences in swimming strokes. Polydactylism.</p> 
<p>Has just sent Hooker a paper on Sikkim tree-ferns [<hi rend="italic">Trans. Linn. Soc. Lond.</hi> 30 (1875): 1–44, read 1870].</p> 
            <p>Has had fever since the end of the rains.</p>
        </abstract>
